        <Parent_String>Sarcoramphus (genus) [300404852], Cathartidae (family) [300387558], Falconiformes (order) [300310286], Aves (class) [300266506], Vertebrata (subphylum) [300265720], Chordata (phylum) [300266513], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
